    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Your art can infect the chakra network of an affected creature. Creature who fail their saving throw vs your art, or whom you would score a successful hit with your art, has their chakra network invaded by your cursed chakra. They take Chakra damage equal to the damage you deal with your art.</p><p>Additionally, for until the end of their next turn, jutsu they cast have their cost tripled for the duration.</p>",
